    "content": "The correct order of reactivity for the addition reaction of the following carbonyl compounds with ethylmagnesium iodide is <br><br><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1l8hrnmdw/d6147c06-a4f4-4a93-9996-ceb1ca5c6f6a/d36b4d40-3d0c-11ed-9b24-3751e41e0789/file-1l8hrnmdx.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1l8hrnmdw/d6147c06-a4f4-4a93-9996-ceb1ca5c6f6a/d36b4d40-3d0c-11ed-9b24-3751e41e0789/file-1l8hrnmdx.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"WB JEE 2018 Chemistry - Aldehyde and Ketone Question 8 English\">",
    "options": [
