    "content": "Amongst the following compounds, the one that will not respond to Cannizzaro reaction upon treatment with alkali is ",
    "options": [
      {
        "identifier": "A",
        "content": "Cl<sub>3</sub>CCHO"
      },
      {
        "identifier": "B",
        "content": "Me<sub>3</sub>CCHO"
      },
      {
        "identifier": "C",
